@unnumberedsubsec Comparator error

@deftp {Condition Object Type} &inexact-real-comparator-with-ignored-epsilon
Used to signal that a non-false @var{epsilon} argument was used with a
symbolic @var{rounding} argument in the call to
@func{make-inexact-real-comparator}: in this case @var{epsilon} is
ignored.

It has the following fields:

@table @code
@item epsilon
The @var{epsilon} argument.

@item rounding
